{"id":239616,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-湖北数位访民到中南海喊冤一人被抓（图/","date":"2012-07-13T02:31:16Z","modified":"2012-07-13T02:31:16Z","title":"维权网 | 湖北数位访民到中南海喊冤一人被抓（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span> </span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><br /><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员关小令报道）据湖北省襄樊市访民郭怀秀说，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日下午</span><span>，湖北省襄樊市数位在京访民前往中南海喊冤时，一人被抓后关进黑监狱控制，数人成功逃离。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当天被抓的访民王有华，是因带有一个几岁的外甥女，无法快跑而被抓，目前被当地政府关押在驻京办控制。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>访民王有华是因她丈夫被黑社会枪杀后，公安办假案，法院又枉判，申诉上访至今无果，还多次被关黑监狱迫害。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>其中一位跑掉的湖北省襄樊市访民江富友，曾是襄樊市便衣警察，因秉公办案，得罪有关领导涉案亲属遭报复，不明不白失去工作，又因不徇私情办案，使涉案妻侄被抓，导致离婚，其身强体壮的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>岁儿子江俊超于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>时</span><span>许，不明原因死于襄阳炫动时刻体育健身有限公司，要求公安做尸检，公安要江富友交一万元尸检费为由卡着不做尸检，且儿子死后财产也不知去向，为此导致江富友上访申诉无果，反受政府和公安机关的非法关押和残酷迫害。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>下旬，正在北京上访的江富友，被地方政府花钱雇佣数十位不明身份人，用车将他拦截绑架关押数日后，于当月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日押送回襄阳区后，投进政府设在熊营村一处所谓“法制教育班”</span><span> </span><span>中囚禁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>，江富友再次被抓进熊营村“法制教育班”，</span><span> </span><span>当晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>时许，有三名警察对他审讯施刑逼供，要其承认是非法上访，一位佩戴警号为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">069555</span><span>的警察用双手卡住江的颈脖进行辱骂。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>夜晚，政府又雇请</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>多名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>岁左右年青人对江实施暴力毒打，并警告说：“大叔，你莫怪我们打你，我们是政府出钱请来教训你的。”在场看守的区政法委干部凶狠地说：“打死你也没人作证，看你还敢去北京告我们。”江被囚禁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>天后，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>又被公安转押入拘留所予以行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>天，再转押进“法制教育班”</span><span> </span><span>囚禁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>天后放出。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日</span><span>，江富友突然又被两名公安领着居委会和办事处的十多名干部突然光临住房，砸开门锁将他抓进“法制教育班”</span><span> </span><span>囚禁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>天，并逼迫他签下永不上访合同后才放出。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>访民江富友表示，在这个没有法律保障公民生命权的今天，为了给被谋杀儿子讨个公道，为保护自己的合法权益，决心不惜生命来捍卫人权。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-nAU4WO2p3lY/T_-EwAhar2I/AAAAAAAAJOk/fFiIehnfi44/s1600/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8A%93%E5%85%B3%E9%BB%92%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%8B%E6%9C%89%E5%8D%8E.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-nAU4WO2p3lY/T_-EwAhar2I/AAAAAAAAJOk/fFiIehnfi44/s320/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8A%93%E5%85%B3%E9%BB%92%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%8B%E6%9C%89%E5%8D%8E.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>被抓关黒监狱的王有华</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-MNf9J0Qz7zM/T_-EzcOLt3I/AAAAAAAAJOs/SR2Ihy6GTOc/s1600/%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E6%B1%9F%E5%AF%8C%E5%8F%8B.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-MNf9J0Qz7zM/T_-EzcOLt3I/AAAAAAAAJOs/SR2Ihy6GTOc/s1600/%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E6%B1%9F%E5%AF%8C%E5%8F%8B.JPG\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>访民江富友</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKctOwTQbm0/T_-E6Ae6S0I/AAAAAAAAJO0/f58FuVEtS14/s1600/DSCF6017.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKctOwTQbm0/T_-E6Ae6S0I/AAAAAAAAJO0/f58FuVEtS14/s320/DSCF6017.JPG\" width=\"232\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-2371900460481978043?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/4561ec0d89E58D8E.JPG-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}